body: I was looking through a recent panic log (and verified it's here as well) is a leveldb compactionError. So I wiped the index and had it rebuild in case something got fixed previously and my index had some issue. Didn't fix it.
@vrillusions There will always be a goroutine named compactionError in the back trace, so that's fine. If you have the same "panic: leveldb: not found", it's probably the same issue. Otherwise, not.
